# Patterns

Source of truth: @ai/rules/common/patterns.md

## Quick Rules

- No `any` without an inline comment justifying it
- Prefer `unknown` + narrowing over `any` at boundaries
- Validate external data shape before use (API responses, deep links, storage reads)
- Async: `Promise.all` for independent calls — no sequential `await` waterfalls
- Error handling: never empty catch; log + user-facing message + classify (network/auth/validation)
- Never log tokens, passwords, auth headers, or PII
- No dynamic string construction with untrusted input (injection)
- Early return to flatten nesting
